<div class="title">In Moderation It's Perfect</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=sarah&Exact=1">sarah</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; sarah. "In Moderation It's Perfect: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) (exp46567)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 11, 2008. erowid.org/exp/46567</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
